comments: Okongwu (ATL) establishes himself in Harris' (ORL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.

Murray (ATL) brings his right hand forward and marginal contact occurs with Banchero's (ORL) front as he changes direction after his gather. Okongwu (ATL) then makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Banchero prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Okongwu (ATL) engages and disengages with Wagner (ORL) during the inbound.
Murray (ATL) does not re-establish in bounds prior to making contact with the ball on the baseline.
Bogdanovic (ATL) establishes verticality and legally contests Wagner's (ORL) layup attempt.
Harris (ORL) extends laterally and does not establish a legal guarding position prior to body contact occurring as Young (ATL) starts his dribble.
Harris (ORL) turns slightly prior to marginal body contact occurring with Young (ATL) as Young dribbles along the sideline.
Banchero (ORL) brushes Young's (ATL) right arm and marginal contact occurs as Young drives toward the lane.
Wagner (ORL) moves toward Hunter (ATL) and marginal side-to-side contact occurs as the errant pass is made.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Young (ATL) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Wagner (ORL) brings his hands toward Hunter's (ATL) side and marginal contact occurs as Wagner releases away to roll.
Banchero (ORL) and Murray (ATL) turn toward one another and marginal body contact occurs as they each pursue the rebound.
Possession is awarded to Orlando after Bogdanovic (ATL) deflects the pass along the sideline. However, the ball never touches the boundary line and play should have remained live.
Bogdanovic (ATL) turns to go over the screen and marginal body contact occurs as he and Wagner (ORL) come together. Wagner then draws attention to the contact.
Wagner (ORL) establishes himself in a wide screening position and initiates foot contact with Hunter (ATL) that causes him to trip.
Okongwu's (ATL) left arm comes forward slightly and marginal contact occurs with Banchero's (ORL) left arm as he attempts the layup.

Harris (ORL) brushes Young's (ATL) left arm after his gather and marginal contact occurs. Banchero (ORL) is turning away from Young prior to marginal contact occurring with Young's slightly extended forearm after the release. Banchero avoids making contact with Young's head as Banchero follows through on his shot contest.
Okongwu (ATL) raises his right arm up as he pursues the rebound and incidental contact occurs with Wagner's (ORL) left arm as he secures the ball.

Hunter (ATL) is moving alongside Fultz's (ORL) path when marginal body contact occurs prior to Fultz's gather.
Hunter (ATL) and Murray (ATL) legally contest Fultz's (ORL) driving shot attempt.
